  "title": "Senior Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Responsible for quantity surveying, BOQ, supplier and sub-contractor management</li>\n  <li>Prepare the subcontractor bill of quantities, specifications, contracts and programmes and schedules for the tender/works</li>\n  <li>Monitor and measure contractors works and assist the QS to certify valuations</li>\n  <li>Preparation of Cost value reports</li>\n  <li>Ensure the periodic reviews of suppliers and sub-contractors</li>\n  <li>Attend daily and monthly meetings</li>\n  <li>Ensure contractors conform to and submit all relevant SHEP documents as necessary</li>\n  <li>Preparation of project budgets and monitor the monthly actuals against planned</li>\n  <li>Provide technical information on specifications supply and logistics arrangements facilitating efficient procurement, clearance, storage and distribution of supplies and equipment</li>\n  <li>Ensure drawings and designs meet project/tender deadlines</li>\n  <li>Exposure to various industry design CAD practices and work cultures </li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R22110981</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Name: Law Mei Fong</p>",
